statements.sql:
SELECT `comment`.`data`,
`comment`.content,
`comment`.grade,
`comment`.bid,
`comment`.uid,
business.id,
business.`name`,
dealer.id,
business.did
FROM `comment`, `user`, business, dealer
WHERE `comment`.uid = `user`.id AND `comment`.uid = business.id AND dealer.id = business.did
